com.ephesoft.dcma.docassembler.classification.searchablepdf

Class SearchablePdfClassification

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ephesoft.dcma.docassembler.classification.searchablepdf.SearchablePdfClassification
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DocumentClassification

    public class SearchablePdfClassification
extends java.lang.Object
implements DocumentClassification
    This class does the actual processing on the basis of SearchablePdfClassification for document assembly. It modifies the document type in batch xml created in searchable pdf workflow so that it can be process by multipage process.
